{"tid":1421032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"811深水埗遊行","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T18:22:29.000Z","uid":201861,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2801390c33d48edb578063c1be93d3eec184e77c","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QRy9jN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QRy9jN.jpg&h=074b4b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n．8 11深水埗區接力開花<br />\n．5大訴求缺一不可<br />\n．掃走黑幫，還我香港<br />\n．踢走黑警，公義城市<br />\n．香港人覺醒🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗遊行公海<br />\n@sspo811<br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗遊行頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ssp811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fssp811&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=9743d7fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ssp811</a><br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗遊行義工群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NYjxo0Uoem5ZO1f2jJUdAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNYjxo0Uoem5ZO1f2jJUdAg&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=f8c8b475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NYjxo0Uoem5ZO1f2jJUdAg</a><br />\n<br />\n．集合地點：楓樹街球場<br />\n．集合時間：1430<br />\n．出發時間：1500<br />\n．終點：深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n路線：<br />\n楓樹街➡️長沙灣道➡️興華街➡️深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n．全民集結，還我香港🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n＊仍待不反對通知書申請中，已與警察再三會面，並讓步更改路線。<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港人廣傳，支持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日85三罷 入夜深水埗開戰<br />\n即使有大量街坊喺度都照放tear gas<br />\n完全冇理會身處嘅環境周遭有大量民居<br />\n街坊圍觀嘅 路過嘅 都係完全冇gear 口罩都冇<br />\n絕對唔係全部full gear<br />\n希望大家811支持港島區遊行之餘 可以黎深水埗行<br />\n大家 811見<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不分化<br />\n槍口對外 目標一致<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港加油 各區加油 手足們加油<br />\nBe Water, Hit and Run"},{"pid":"d97eacb798dd63ccf1379a3d7781151719e48ef8","tid":1421032,"uid":15380,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"深水埗警署係二級歷史文物"},{"pid":"5cf591ae7aea4c1c7f3d52f345c93f92bf12cd6f","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"9239b59ccfeeadecfc7fe59f0ff85a0c0c811bab","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"d2e972aedb8b52d7469bc93faf5707354a753cf3","tid":1421032,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85202f664b1a7999d3a89f0da067747e4300d7ac","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"不撤不散"},{"pid":"ce27f23ba8558648b7d806f0e8eee0ce37ff5f8a","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0e97689d89611a59cdbe869fb361c6904a5b41ca","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f3b85bc2efe548e7190e413e90224daf8aa02d0","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6552b1f2870e9ae3c65434195498c4067a3cbd0","tid":1421032,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d97eacb798dd63ccf1379a3d7781151719e48ef8","tid":1421032,"uid":15380,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"深水埗警署係二級歷史文物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"分分鐘去太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b507b510414006d72aff5e73a78ae098dc3aa1","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15012f9a64dce35ccfcd683f69b38f218dece6c","tid":1421032,"uid":201861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6552b1f2870e9ae3c65434195498c4067a3cbd0","tid":1421032,"uid":108467,"like"